prompts.frontCover: A flat 2D cartoon illustration of a humorous beach scene for a birthday card, in a botanical art style. In the center, cartoon versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are comically attempting to build a giant, lopsided sandcastle. Lao Lao, wearing her light blue sweatshirt, is laughing as she places a crooked tower on top, while Jordan, in his tan hoodie, pretends to be a serious architect, holding up a seashell like a blueprint. Surrounding them is not sand, but a beautiful botanical pattern of illustrated monsteras, palm fronds, and hibiscus flowers that seamlessly blends into the beach, with gentle turquoise waves in the background. A mischievous cartoon seagull wearing a tiny party hat is trying to steal a sand bucket. The overall color palette is bright and cheerful with soft, natural tones. In the center of the card, floating in a clear area, is the text "Happy Birthday, lao lao!" written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script.
